Images: ["[630_360_16813...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1681312286-744.jpg)", "[1681312286-44...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1681312286-446.jpg)"]

