[![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-04-12T64-00-00-04-00/11-3-150x150.jpg)](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-3.jpg)

[![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-04-12T64-00-00-04-00/12-2-150x150.jpg)](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-2.jpg)

[![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-04-12T64-00-00-04-00/13-2-150x150.jpg)](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/13-2.jpg)

